{
  "stem": "19550.3",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He could tolerate no compromise when it came to-- what he could say to Judaism.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There was either his way or no way at all.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Anything that in the slightest way departed from his conception of Judaism was beyond the pale of Judaism and could not be tolerated, certainly in his own family.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And he, he would make no compromises.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "He couldn't.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "To him, the slightest compromise would have been tantamount to hypocrisy.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And, you know, it's-- he was very intolerant in that sense.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It-- my relationship with my father was, in retrospect, I, I guess I should call it very unfortunate because [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I was no less devoted and dedicated to Judaism, in my perception and my conception of Judaism, and certainly in the perpetuation of Jews and Judaism, and I was as determined and as stiff-necked in my way as he was in his way.",
      "word_count": 66
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The result was that since I was thoroughly Jewish, I was more than happy to attempt to study and meet him on the level of rabbinic studies.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] But beyond that point, when it came to observance or when it came to our relationship, so to say, to the outside world, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] there was a complete disjuncture between my father and myself.",
      "word_count": 41
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "There was absolutely no relationship.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So my relationship to with my father, I would say, could be summarized by a-- an ongoing contest between myself and him.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I wanted to demonstrate to him that I could be as knowledgeable in Judaism as he was or that he wanted me to be without being observant as he was.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Were there any activities that you participated in that he would not have sanctioned?",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
